Package: kde-i18n-frisian
Version: 3.5.3
Revision: 12
Description: KDE - language files for Frisian
License: GPL/LGPL
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <kde-i18n-frisian@fink.racoonfink.com>

Depends: kdelibs3-unified (>= %v-11), xfonts-intl
BuildDepends: fink (>= 0.24-1), arts-dev, kdebase3-unified-dev (>= %v-11), kdelibs3-unified-dev (>= %v-11), libxml2, libxslt, xfonts-intl
Replaces: koffice-i18n-frisian, khangman, kturtle

Source: mirror:kde:stable/%v/src/kde-i18n/kde-i18n-fy-%v.tar.bz2
SourceDirectory: kde-i18n-fy-%v
Source-MD5: c64d0ff6d11d4b9780416bb3375fd683
PatchScript: perl -pi -e 's,doc/HTML,doc/kde,g' configure

CompileScript: (export HOME=/tmp; export KDEDIR=%p; sh configure %c; find . -name \*.bz2 -exec touch {} \;; make -j2)

InstallScript: <<
  make -j2 install DESTDIR=%d
  mkdir -p %i/share/doc/kde-installed-packages
  touch %i/share/doc/kde-installed-packages/kde-i18n-frisian
<<

DescDetail: Language files for the K Desktop Environment: Frisian

